createConverter(address,address,uint32,a.details: creates a new converter with the given arguments and transfers the ownership and management to the sender.

params._connectorToken: optional, initial connector, allows defining the first connector at deployment time
params._connectorWeight: optional, weight for the initial connector
params._maxConversionFee: maximum conversion fee, represented in ppm
params._registry: address of a contract registry contract
params._token: smart token governed by the converter
